`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Scry
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * scry <target>

 This skill for fighter types is similar to the locate person spell that
spellcasters possess. One difference is that the target of this skill will see
a message on their screen alerting them to the fact they have been located.

